raw_meta_yaml:
context:
  name: mkdocs-marimo
  version: "0.2.1"

package:
  name: ${{ name|lower }}
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  - url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/${{ name[0] }}/${{ name }}/mkdocs_marimo-${{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 9e4cf8005b79856beb3e9db48e7c8fa7f94a5d00c05aa6877f44a173c0ec9bb0

build:
  script: python -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - python ${{ python_min }}.*
    - pip
    - hatchling
  run:
    - python >=${{ python_min }}
    - htmlmin2 >=0.1.13,<0.2
    - marimo >=0.8.15
    - mkdocs >=1.5.2,<2

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - mkdocs_marimo
      pip_check: true
      python_version: ${{ python_min }}

about:
  homepage: https://github.com/marimo-team/mkdocs-marimo
  summary: MkDocs marimo plugin
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: LICENSE
  repository: https://github.com/marimo-team/mkdocs-marimo
  documentation: https://marimo-team.github.io/mkdocs-marimo

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pavelzw
